io.doov.core.dsl.field

Interface BaseFieldInfo<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the field value
    All Superinterfaces:
    DslField<T>, Readable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    LogicalFieldInfo, NumericFieldInfo<N>, TemporalFieldInfo<N>, TextFieldInfo
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BooleanFieldInfo, CharacterFieldInfo, DateIsoFieldInfo, DefaultFieldInfo, DoubleFieldInfo, EnumFieldInfo, FloatFieldInfo, IntegerFieldInfo, IterableFieldInfo, LocalDateFieldInfo, LocalDateTimeFieldInfo, LocalTimeFieldInfo, LongFieldInfo, StringFieldInfo, TimeIsoFieldInfo

    public interface BaseFieldInfo<T>
extends DslField<T>
    Base interface for all field info.

    It contains default methods for common checks, which are calls to methods on DefaultCondition.

    See Also:
    DslField.getDefaultFunction()
